{
  "texts": [
    "Manual review of notesAll notes with stressful events detected by LLM and an additional 50 notes with no events detected were manually reviewed to assess precision and recall of extraction and to ensure that only correct events are used in logistic regression analysis.",
    "The review was performed by a single human reviewer (DS) who was using a guideline validated by other team members to ensure consistent review.",
    "The guideline was based on the prompt that the LLM used but included more examples.",
    "For instance, the event \"experienced abuse as a child or lived in problematic household\" was elaborated by providing specific cases (drug/alcohol usage in the household, violence between guardians, verbal abuse, sexual abuse, physical abuse).In addition, the precision of extraction of date of event was evaluated on a subset of 100 notes.",
    "Events affecting a small number of patients (< 10) were excluded from the population table and odds ratio analysis."
  ]
}